\id 1TH Meitei: Roman Script 1st Translation
\h 1 Thessalonians
\toc1 THESSALONICA-GI Misingda I-ba Paul-gi Ahanba Chitthi
\toc2 1 Thessalonica
\toc3 1 Thess
\mt1 THESSALONICA-GI
\mt2 Misingda I-ba Paul-gi Ahanba Chitthi
\imt1 Wahoudok
\ip Thessalonica-da i-ba ahanba chithi asi pakhonchatpa Paul-na ibani (1:1). Bible-gi saruk ama oirakkhiba Paul-gi chithisinggi marakta masina Pual-na i-ba ahanba chithi oibasu yai aduga masi Christtana poklaba matung chahi 51 gi matungda ikhibani. Mahakki anisuba khongchatta lingkhatlamba Thessalonica-gi singlup asida chithi asi i-ba matamda Paul Corinth-da leirammi (Pakhon 17:1-10). Singlup asi Jihudi kharaga Greek-ki mi mayam amagana punsillaga sembani haina Pakhonchatpasinggi thabak-ki lairikta hairi.
\ip Paul-na singlup asi lingkhatlaba matung matam kuina mahakna Thessalonica-da leiba phanglamde, maram aduna mapham aduda leiriba thajabasingda pukning thougatnabagidamak chithi asi thakhibani. Chithi asida hiram kayamarum ama yaori aduga christiansingna kamdouna hinggadage haibagi maramda achamba paotak kayamarumsu yaori. Paul-na masida Christtana amuk lengbirakkadaba adugi maramda pukning chingsilli. Thessalonica-gi singlupta leiba thajabasingna akaknana hiram asida yamna thawai yaorambasu yai. Tengban Mapuna penbiba punsi ama hingnaba insinba oina Christtana aniraksuba oina lengbirakkadaba adubu sijinnei (5:6-8).
\iot Yaopham Takpa
\io1 1. Singluppu khurumjaba amadi makhoigidamak Tengban Mapu thagatchabaga loinana Paul-na chithi asi houba \ior (1)\ior*
\io1 2. Adudagi mahakna mahakki thabakki maramda amadi Timothy-na purakpa pao adugi maramda sandokna takpa \ior (2–3)\ior*
\io1 3. Mathangda Christtana aniraksuba oina lengbirakkadaba aduda yengduna Christiansingna kamdouna hingadage haibagi paotak piba \ior (4:1–5:15)\ior*
\io1 4. Singluppu amuk hanna khurumjaduna amadi singlupta leiriba mioi khudingmakna chithi asi sungsoi soidana pahan-gadabani haibaga loinana chithi asi loisinba \ior (5:16-28)\ior*
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Paul, Silas amadi Timothy-na,
\p Thessalonica-da leiriba, Mapa Ibungo Tengban Mapu amadi Ibungo Jisu Christtagi singlupta:
\p Thoujal amadi ingthaba nakhoida leisanu.
\s1 Thessalonica-da leiba Christiansinggi punsi amadi thajaba
\p 
\v 2 Matam pumnamakta eikhoina nakhoi pumnamakkidamak Tengban Mapubu thagatchei amasung eikhoina haija-haijaba matamda nakhoigidamak matam pumnamkta ningsingjei.
\v 3 Maramdi karamna nakhoigi thajaba adubu nakhoina thabakta onthokpa, nakhoigi nungsiba aduna nakhoibu kayada kanna nomhalliba, amadi Ibungo Jisu Christtada leiba nakhoigi asha aduna nakhoibu kayada khangheiba oihalliba haibadu eikhoigi Tengban Mapu amasung Ipagi mangda eikhoina ningsingjei.
\v 4 Ichil inaosa, Tengban Mapuna nakhoibu nungsibi amasung masamakki mi oinanaba nakhoibu khandokpire haiba eikhoina khang-i.
\v 5 Maramdi eikhoina nakhoida Aphaba Pao purakpa adu wahei khaktana natte, adubu madu panggalga loinana, Thawai Asengbaga loinana amasung masigi achumba asi sungsoi soidre haibaga loinana nakhoida purakkhibani. Nakhoiga leiminnaringei matamda eikhoina karamna hingkhibage haibadu nakhoina khang-i; madu nakhoigi phananabagidamaktani.
\v 6 Nakhoina eikhoigi amasung Ibungogi matou loukhi, maramdi nakhoina awa anang kaya khanglaba phaobada nakhoina Thawai Asengbadagi lakpa haraoba aduga loinana wa adubu lousinjakhi.
\v 7 Maram aduna nakhoina Macedonia amasung Achaia-da leiba thajaba ichil inao pumnamakta matou tamjanapham oirakle.
\v 8 Maramdi Ibungogi wa adu Macedonia amadi Achaia khaktada nakhoidagi sandokkhibakhak nattaduna, nakhoina Tengban Mapu thajabagi pao adu mapham pumnamakta thungkhre. Maram aduna eikhoina madugi maramda karisu hainingai mathou tadre.
\v 9 Maramdi matou karamna nakhoina eikhoibu lousinbikhibage haibadu makhoi masamakna tamlare. Nakhoina kamdouna lai-murtidagi ahingba amadi achumba Tengban Mapubu thougal tounanaba Tengban Mapuda onsillakkhiba,
\v 10 Amasung mahakki machanupa aduna haibadi mahakna sibadagi hinggat-hanbikhiba amasung lakkadouriba Tengban Mapugi asaoba adudagi eikhoibu kanbiba mahakki machanupa Jisu aduna swarga-thaktagi lenglakpa adubu nakhoina ngaijaba adu makhoina tamle.
\c 2
\s1 Thessalonica-da Paul-na thougal touba
\p 
\v 1 Ichil inaosa, eikhoina nakhoigi nanakta lakkhiba adu aremba natte haiba nakhoi nasamakna khang-i.
\v 2 Eikhoina Thessalonica-da nakhoigi nanakta laktringeigi mamangda kamdouna eikhoibu Philippi saharda thina toubikhiba amadi ikaiba nanghankhiba haibadu nakhoina khang-i. Adubu ayet-apan kaya ama leiraba phaobada eikhoigi Tengban Mapuna nakhoida Ibungo mangondagi lakpa Aphaba Pao adu haidoknaba eikhoida thouna pinabikhi.
\v 3 Eikhoigi haijaba adu asoiba nattraga sengdaba wakhallonda yumpham oiba natte aduga eikhoina kanagumba amatabu lounamnaba hotnade.
\v 4 Madugi mahutta, Tengban Mapuna eikhoida phongdok-hanba pamba adu eikhoina matam pumnamakta ngang-i, Maramdi Aphaba Pao adu sinnabada matik chaba ama oina Tengban Mapuna eikhoibu leppire. Eikhoina misingbu pelhannaba hotnade adubu eikhoigi thamoibu chang yengbiba Tengban Mapubu pelhannaba eikhoina sandok-i.
\v 5 Eikhoina keidoungeidasu mibu thagatsannaba wahei sijinnade, aduga kaarambabu kupsinnaba tousinnaba wasu sijinade haiba nakhoina khang-i. Tengban Mapuna eikhoigi sakhini.
\v 6 Christtagi pakhonchatpa ama oina eikhoina eikhoigi matik adu sijinnaba yaramlabasu, eikhoina nakhoidagi oirabasu kana amadagi oirabasu misingdagi eikhoina thagatpiba phangnaba hotnajade.
\v 7 Adubu eikhoina nakhoigi narakta leiringei matamda mamana machasingbu luna channa toujabagumna eikhoina pukning tapna leijarammi.
\v 8 Eikhoina nakhoibu asukki matik nungsijaba maramna, Tengban Mapugi Aphaba Pao adu khakta nattaduna eikhoigi punsi asi phaobasu nakhoida pithokpada eikoina harao-nungaijakhi.
\v 9 Ichil inaosa, eikhoigi kanna nomba amasung tamthina waba adu nakhoina soidana ningsinglamgani; eikhoina nakhoida Tengban Mapugi Aphaba pao sandoklingei matamduda nakhoi kana amatada potlum oihandanaba eikhoina ahing nungthil naidana thabak sukhi.
\p 
\v 10 Thajaba nakhoigi narakta kayada sengna, chumna amadi ayol aran leitana eikhoina chatkhibage haibadu nakhoinasu amasung Tengban Mapunasu sakhini.
\v 11 Mapa amana masamakki machasingbu loinabagumna eikhoina nakhoi khudingmakka loinakhi haibadu nakhoina khang-i.
\v 12 Ibungo mahak masamakki leibaak amasung matik mangal adubu saruk phangminnanaba nakhoibu koubiba Tengban Mapubu pelhanba punsi mahing aduda hingnanaba eikhoina nakhoibu thougatchakhi, themjinjakhi amadi taksinduna leikhi.
\p 
\v 13 Aduga eikhoina karigidamak matam pumbada Tengban Mapubu thagatcharibano haibagi atoppa maram amasu leiri. Madudi eikhoina nakhoida Tengban Mapugi paojel adu purakpa matamda nakhoina madubu takhi amasung mioibadagi lakpa paojel amagum nattaduna tasengnamak Tengban Mapugi waheisu oiriba paojel adubu nakhoina Tengban Mapugi paojel oina lousinjakhi. Maramdi thajaba nakhoida Tengban Mapuna thabak toubiri.
\v 14 Aduga Ichil inaosa, nakhoisu Judea-gi Christta Jisuda leiba Tengban Mapugi singlupsing adugi matou loubasing oirakle: Singlupsing aduna Jihudisinggi makhuttagi awa ana khangkhiba aduga mannana nakhoinasu nakhoi nasamakki misinggi maphamdagi awa ana khaangle.
\v 15 Jihudising aduna Ibungo Jisubu amadi Tengban Mapugi wa phongdokpibasing adubu hatkhi, aduga eikhoibu ot-neibikhi. Makhoina Tengban Mapubu kayada pelhandriba! Makhoina mi pumnamakta kayada yengthiriba!
\v 16 Jihudi nattaba phurupsingda aran-khubham purakkadaba paojel adubu eikhoina makhoida sandokpa adu phaoba makhoina thingnaba hotnakhi. Matou asumna makhoina touba pap pumnamak adu maton lomhalle. Aduga houjik Tengban Mapugi asaoba adu akonbada makhoigi mathakta lakle.
\s1 Paul-na Thessalonica-da amuk lakningba
\p 
\v 17 Ichil inaosa, matam khara nakhoidagi eikhoina tonganna leikhiba matam aduda, (thamoigi oinadi lapnakhide adubu hakchanggi khakta oinani), eikhoigi oinadi, eikhoina nakhoibu kayada inakta leihanningkhiba aduga nakhoibu amuk unnanaba eikhoina kayada kanna hotnakhiba!
\v 18 Maramdi eikhoina nakhoigi nanakta amuk lakpa pamkhi. Paul eihak isamaknasu hanna hanna laknaba hotnakhi, adubu Satan-na eikhoigi lambi thingkhi.
\v 19 Maramdi, eikhoigi asha, eikhoigi haraojapham amadi Ibungo Jisu Christtana lengbirakpa matamda Ibungogi mangda eikhoigi chaothokchapham oigadouriba luhup adu karino? Madu nakhoi nattabra?
\v 20 Tasengnamak, nakhoidi eikhoigi chaothokchapham amasung haraojapham aduni.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Akonbada, eikhoina makha tana khaangba ngamdrabada, eikhoi khakta Athens-ta leihoubana phagani haina eikhoina leple.
\v 2 Aduna Christtagi Aphaba Pao sandokpada eikhoiga loinana Tengban Mapugi thougal touminnaba ichil inao Timothy-bu nakhoigi thajaba adu kankhat-hannaba amadi thougatnaba eikhoina thare.
\v 3 Madu nakhoi kana amatana ot neiba adugi maramna mai leithoktanabani. Asigumba awa anangsing asi eikhoigidamak Tengban Mapugi aningbagi saruk amani haiba nakhoi nasamaknasu khang-i.
\v 4 Maramdi eikhoina nakhoiga leiminnaringei matamda, eikhoibu ot-neigadouri haibasi eikhoina nakhoida mangajounana haikhre; aduga madumak thoklare haiba adu nakhoinasu khanglibadu mangai.
\v 5 Maram adugidamak, eina makha tathana khaangba ngamdrabada, eina nakhoigi thajabagi maramda khangnanaba Timothy-bu thakhibani. Maramdi athemba mapu aduna karigumba upai ama touduna nakhoibu themdoklamgadra aduga eikhoigi nomjaba pumnamak aremba taragadra haina eina kirammi.
\p 
\v 6 Adubu houjik Timothy-na nakhoigi naphamdagi hallaktuna nakhoigi thajaba amasung nungsibagi maramda nungaiba pao purakle. Aduga matam pumnamakta nakhoina eikhoibu ningsingbi amasung eikhoina nakhoibu yamna uningba adugumna nakhoinasu eikhoibu uningngi haina mahakna eikhoida tamlare.
\v 7 Maram aduna ichil inaosa, nakhoigi thajaba adugi maramna nakhoina eikhoigi awa ana amadi otpi neibiba pumnamakta eikhoibu pukning thougatpire.
\v 8 Maramdi nakhoina Ibungoda chetna leppagi maramna houjikti eikhoi tasengna hingli.
\v 9 Houjik nakhoigidamak eikhoina eikhoigi Tengban Mapubu thagatchaba ngamjare. Nakhoigi maramna Tengban Mapugi mangda eikhoina phangjariba harao nungaibasing asigidamak Ibungo mahakpu eikhoina thagatchei.
\v 10 Eikoina nakhoibu amuk hanna ujanaba amadi nakhoigi thajabada awatpa leiriba adu menkhatnaba Tengban Mapugi maphamda ahing nungthil naidana pukning changna Tengban da haijari.
\p 
\v 11 Eikhoigi Tengban Mapu, Ipa masamakna amasung eikhoigi Ibungo Jisuna nakhoigi nanakta eikhoina laknabagi lambi ama thourangbiba oisanu.
\v 12 Eikhoina nakhoibu nungsibagunmna Ibungona nakhoi amaga amagagi marakta amadi mi pumnamakta nakhoigi nungsiba adu hen-gat-hanbisanu amadi pathok-hanbisanu.
\v 13 Asumna eikhoigi Ibungo Jisuna mahakki asengba mi pumnamakka loinana lenglakpa matamda eikhoigi Tengban Mapu amasung Ipagi mangda nakhoina mapung phana ayol aran leitaba amasung asengba oinanaba Ibungo mahakna nakhoibu panggal kankhat-hanbigani.
\c 4
\s1 Tengban Mapubu pelhanba punsi
\p 
\v 1 Aroibada, ichil inaosa, Tengban Mapubu pelhannabagidamak nakhoina kamdouna hinggadage haiba adu nakhoina eikhoidagi khangle. Tasengnamak nakhoina hingliba punsi adusu madumakni. Aduga madudagi thoidok hendoknasu tounaba eikhoina nakhoida Ibungo Jisugi mingda haijari aduga thousu thoujanjari.
\v 2 Maramdi Ibungo Jisugi matikki mapanna eikhoina nakhoida kari paotak pikhiba nakhoina khang-i.
\v 3 Nakhoina asengba oiba amadi nupa nupi lannaba pumtha thadokpa adu Tengban Mapuna pammi.
\v 4 Madudi nakhoi khudingmakna asengba amadi ikaikhumnaba mawongda nasagi hakchangbu khudum chanba tamjagadabani.
\v 5 Tengban Mapu khangdaba atoppa phurupsinggumna hakchanggi oiba tinnaningbagi apambada luptasanu.
\v 6 Hiram asida kana amatana christian machil manaoda aranba toudasanu aduga khudongchaba loudasanu. Eikhoina masi nakhoida hannasu haikhre, aduga eikhoina akanba cheksinwasu haikhre madudi adugumna touba makhoising adugi mathakta Ibungona cheirak pigani.
\v 7 Maramdi Tengban Mapuna eikhoibu sengdaba oinanaba koubiba natte, adubu asengba punsi amada hingnanaba koubibani.
\v 8 Maram aduna tambiba asibu lousindaba mahak aduna mioibabu yadaba natte, adubu nakhoida Thawai Asengbabu pibiba Tengban Mapubu yadabani.
\p 
\v 9 Houjik, thajabasingna amana amabu nungsinabagi matangdadi eikhoina nakhoida irubagi mathou tadre, maramdi nakhoi nasel amaga amaga nungsinagadabani haibadu nakhoi nasamakta Tengban Mapuna tambire.
\v 10 Aduga, tasengnamaksu nakhoina Macedonia apumbada leiba ichil inao pumnamakta madumak tou-i. Adumakpu Ichil inaosa, madudagi henna hennaphaobasu tounanaba eikhoina nakhoida thoujinjari.
\v 11 Aduga eikhoina nakhoida mamangda haikhibagumna, ingna tapna panba punsi hingba, nasagi nathouda pukning changba amadi nakhutna thabak sujaba haiba asina nakhoigi pandam oihallu.
\v 12 Adu oirabadi nakhoina hingliba mahing aduna thajaba ichil inao nattabasingdagisu ikai-khumnaba phangjagani aduga nakhoida mathou taba pot adugidamak kanadasu tangjararoi.
\s1 Ibungona lenglakpa
\p 
\v 13 Ichil inaosa, nakhoina asha leitaba makhoising adugumna pukning wadananaba sikhraba makhoising adugi maramda achumba adu nakhoina khangba eikhoina pammi.
\v 14 Maramdi Jisu sire amasung sibadagi amuk hinggatkhre haiba eikhoina thajei, adu oiragadi Ibungobu thajaduna sikhrabasing adubu Tengban Mapuna Jisuga loinana amuk pubirakkani haiba eikhoina thajei.
\p 
\v 15 Ibungogi waheigi matung-inna eikhoina nakhoida hairi madudi Ibungona lenglakpa phaoba hingduna leiriba eikhoina sikhraba makhoising adugi mang thana khak chatloi.
\v 16 Maramdi Ibungo masamakna yathanggi kholaoga loinana, athoiba swargadutki khonjel amasung Tengban Mapugi peresinggagi makholga loinana swargathaktagi lengthabirakkani aduga Christtada sikhibasing aduna hanna hougatkani.
\v 17 Adugi matungda hingduna leihouba eikhoibu makhoiga loinana atiyada Ibungobu unanaba leichilthakta punna pukhatpigani. Aduga matou adugumduna eikhoina lomba naidana Ibungoga leiminnagani.
\v 18 Maram aduna waheising asiga loinana nakhoi amaga amaga themjinnou.
\c 5
\s1 Ibungona lengbirakkadaba adugidamak thourang toujaba
\p 
\v 1 Adubu ichil inaosa, masising asi karamba matamda thokkadage haibadugi makum mathagi maramda nakhoida irubagi mathou tadre.
\v 2 Maramdi Ibungogi numit adu huranbana ahingda lakpagum lakkani haiba nakhoi nasamakna ningthina khang-i.
\v 3 Misingna “Pumnamak ingthare amadi khudong thiningai leitre” haina hairingei matamda khanghoudana makhoigi mathakta amang-ata lakkani. Mironbi nupina chaboklamdaida naoyekpagum madu khanghoudana lakkani amasung misingna madudagi nanthokpa ngamloi.
\v 4 Adubu Ichil inaosa, nakhoidi amambada leite aduga numit aduna huranbagumna lakpada nakhoida angakpa pokhalloi.
\v 5 Nakhoi pumnamak mangalgi amadi nungthilgi machasingni. Eikhoidi ahinggisu amambagisu natte.
\v 6 Maram aduna mi ateisinggumna eikhoi tumganusi; adubu mitsing nasingna amadi isabu laksinjaduna leisi.
\v 7 Maramdi tumlibasing aduna ahingda tumbani, aduga yu ngaobasing aduna ahingda ngaobani.
\v 8 Adubu eikhoidi nungthilgi oiba maramna thajaba amasung nungsibana thabakhang oina haptuna amadi aran-khubhamgi asha aduna lan luhup oina uptuna isa khudum chanduna leisi.
\v 9 Maramdi eikhoibu Tengban Mapugi mei houna saoba adu khaangnanaba Tengban Mapuna khandokpa natte adubu eikhoigi Ibungo Jisu Christtagi mapanna aran-khubham phangjanaba eikhoibu khandokpibani.
\v 10 Ibungo mahakna lakpa matamda eikhoina hingba oirabasu siba oirabasu eikhoina mahakka loinana leiminnanaba Ibungona eikhoigidamak sibire.
\v 11 Maram aduna nakhoina houjik touriba adugumna amaga amaga pukning thougatnou amasung amaga amaga tengbangnou.
\s1 Aroiba paotak amasung khurumjaba
\p 
\v 12 Ichil inaosa, nakhoigi narakta thougal touriba, christian-gi punsida nakhoibu chingbiriba amadi paotak pibiribasing adubu nakhoina matik chana ikai khumnanaba eikhoina nakhoida haijari.
\v 13 Makhoina touriba thabakki maramna makhoibu khwaidagi wangna ikai-khumnabiba amadi nungsibibaga loinana loinabiyu. Amasung nakhoi amaga amaga ingthana leiminnou.
\p 
\v 14 Aduga ichil inaosa, eikhoina nakhoida insinjari, thabak suba tanbasingda cheksin wa haibiyu, akibasingbu thougatpiyu, asonbasingbu pangbiyu, mi pumnamakki maphamda kuina khaangbiyu.
\v 15 Kana amatana phattabagidamak phattaba hanganu, adubu matam pumnamakta amana amagidamak amasung mi pumnamakkidamak aphaba tounanaba hotnou.
\p 
\v 16 Matam pumnamakta haraojou,
\v 17 Leppa leitana haijou,
\v 18 Maram khudingmakta thagatchou, maramdi masimak Christta Jisuda hingliba nakhoigi punsida Tengban Mapugi aningbani.
\p 
\v 19 Thawai Asengbabu thingganu.
\v 20 Tengban Mapuna phongdokpiraba wasing adubu usittaba touganu.
\v 21 Pumnamaksing adubu changyeng tou, aphaba adu chetna paiyu,
\v 22 Phattaba makhal pumnamaktagi lapthok-u.
\p 
\v 23 Eikhoida ingthaba pibiriba Tengban Mapuna nakhoibu hiram khudingmakta asengba oihanbisanu. Eikhoigi Ibungo Jisu Christtana lenglakpa matamda nakhoigi thawai, hingba, amasung hakchang apumba ayol aran leitana thambisanu.
\v 24 Nakhoibu koubiba Ibungo mahakna masi toubigani, maramdi mahakti thajaba yabani.
\p 
\v 25 Ichil inaosa, eikhoigidamaktasu haijabiyu.
\p 
\v 26 Asengba chupchaba aduga loinana ichil inao pumnamakpu khurumjari.
\p 
\v 27 Chithi asi ichil inao pumnamakta pabinaba eina Ibungogi matik adugi mapanna yathang piri.
\p 
\v 28 Eikhoigi Ibungo Jisu Christtagi thoujalna nakhoiga loinabisanu.
